  "body": "### Discussed in https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions/35145\r\n\r\n<div type='discussions-op-text'>\r\n\r\n<sup>Originally posted by **eduleon** August  1, 2023</sup>\r\nHey guys, could you add a new OpenAPI configuration in order to set **OAuth scopes**. Something like:\r\n\r\n- `quarkus.smallrye-openapi.oauth2-implicit-scopes`\r\n\r\nWe need this kind of configuration to improve the experience of Swagger UI as **external service/instance** (not the one included in Quarkus).\r\n\r\nCurrent security schema generated (invalid) üëáüèΩ‚ö†Ô∏è \r\n<img width=\"598\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-01 at 11 16 21\" src=\"https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/assets/8863027/77d1a278-3e26-4c4f-9f05-50d8dcbc1cb0\">\r\n</div>",
